唔係用組織身份講/ <span style=\"color: red;\">宣揚個人立場理應係合法</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60316c6174b86cc23c147a702d952e003745e2cb","tid":834834,"uid":42250,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cb1e951d112f719c9f534afe52e82914c68cf4ab","tid":834834,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T16:27:33.000Z","msg":"以本人理解, 社團條例係指明組織<br />\n組織係公安條例係指3人以上<br />\n<br />\n所以用個人身份, 而唔係用組織身份講/ <span style=\"color: red;\">宣揚個人立場理應係合法</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T16:37:55.000Z","msg":"社團 (society)指本條例條文適用的任何會社、公司、一人以上的合夥或組織，不論性質或宗旨為何；  (由1961年第28號第2條代替)"},{"pid":"0c54ae77b63ee02ccdf83b3518b4ab662d3b1b7e","tid":834834,"uid":194298,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T16:46:22.000Z","msg":"屌你老味都戇鳩仲問違唔違法<br />\n<br />\n而家港共就係佢話你違法就違法，駛鳩理你班法律學者<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c12e081cbc8929a6fd333c44e6363f1638cbaaeb","tid":834834,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T16:57:12.000Z","msg":"其實法律系的講師仲點教法律？"}]}